From: Arun Vikas T <vikast@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 17 Jul 2025 13:43:13 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 5/7] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:CP:HOSTAPD: Copy and send SCS data over
 QM framework

Introduce logic to convert Stream Classification Service (SCS)
request data into QoS Management (QM) request data format to
enable further processing of SCS requests and prepare
the data to be send to driver using generic NL80211_CMD_QOS_MGMT.

Update SCS request handler to include this conversion step,
laying the base for future integration with driver QoS operations.

Integrate QoS response flow into SCS handling, including
mapping between SCS and QoS data structures for the response to
get processed in the further changes.

